The actool requires the Contents.json file to have required

http://www.google.com/design/spec now redirects to https://material.io/guidelines/ which is why I changed that.

Thank you for your time! ^ _ ^

Change our license from CC-BY-SA, to CC-BY

We originally licensed these icons under CC-BY-SA because we wanted to make them
available to you to incorporate into your apps, but we didn't want someone to be
able to package them up and resell them as an icon set.  We heard your concerns
about the scope of the share alike obligation.  Our primary goal here is to make
it easy for you to use the icons, so we've changed the license to CC-BY.
Update index for SVG move

Add production SVGs, which address issues #6 and #37

These SVGs have been further optimized for size (whitespace removed), and
removed any non-rendering paths.

The svg/design subdirectories continue to include a non-rendering path outlining
the border of the icon, which is useful for designers when dropping these icons
into tools like Adobe Illustrator or Sketch
